track_notes: This is probably the most scenic route if you want to get away from road for a bit. Plenty of room on top for antennas. This is a radio site, but did not get much QRM from the site on HF.
track_title: Onyx Peak via PCT and the Forestry Road

track_notes: Bushwack up the gully ridge to the summit.
Difficult to make VHF contacts into Los Angeles.  HF is recommended for activations.
